{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1702-08_113","head":{"value":"[Remarques Ingenieuses sur le Portrait de la Reine d’Espagne]","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", août 1702 [tome 11], p. 113-116.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"value":"On a fait une remarque fort ingenieuse sur le Portrait de la Reine d’Espagne. Vous la trouverez dans ce billet.","id":"/div/p"},"quote":{"label":{"value":"A MONSIEUR ***","id":"/div/quote/label"},"p":{"#":[{"#":{"value":"Je me trouvay dernierement dans une Maison, où l’on regardoit un beau Portrait de la Reine d’Espagne. Aprés avoir parlé de la Majesté charmante de cette Princesse ; je remarquay une singularité pour elle. C’est qu’elle est la ","id":"/div/quote/p/#[0]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"seconde","id":"/div/quote/p/#[1]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" fille de Monsieur le Duc de Savoye ; que ce Prince son Pere se nomme Victor Amedée ","id":"/div/quote/p/#[2]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Second","id":"/div/quote/p/#[3]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" : &amp; qu’elle a épousé le Roy d’Espagne, ","id":"/div/quote/p/#[4]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"second","id":"/div/quote/p/#[5]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" fils de Monsieur le Dauphin. Une Muse peut donner du relief à cette remarque. Car en Latin, ","id":"/div/quote/p/#[6]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Secundus, secunda, secundare","id":"/div/quote/p/#[7]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" sont des termes d’un sens heureux &amp; favorable. L’usage en est frequent dans Virgile. ","id":"/div/quote/p/#[8]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tantum fortuna secunda","id":"/div/quote/p/#[9]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":", Æneid. 9. ","id":"/div/quote/p/#[10]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dii incepta secundent.","id":"/div/quote/p/#[11]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" Æneid. 7. ","id":"/div/quote/p/#[12]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Spirate secundi.","id":"/div/quote/p/#[13]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" Æneid. 3. Et en François ","id":"/div/quote/p/#[14]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Seconder","id":"/div/quote/p/#[15]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":", se prend pour aider, favoriser. Voici l’observation mise en œuvre dans des Vers Latins ; &amp; les Vers François qui les imitent autant que la Langue le peut souffrir.","id":"/div/quote/p/#[16]/#"}}]},"quote":[{"label":{"value":"PRO HISPANIÆ REGINA.","id":"/div/quote/quote[0]/label"},"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Illa secunda extat Victoris nata secundi,","id":"/div/quote/quote[0]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/quote[0]/lg/l[1]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Delphini natus, quamque secundus habet.","id":"/div/quote/quote[0]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Augurium felix ! Expetit fata secunda","id":"/div/quote/quote[0]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/quote[0]/lg/l[3]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Nunc Iber : hæc Regis bellica gesta dabunt.","id":"/div/quote/quote[0]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"label":{"#1":{"value":"POUR LA REINE","id":"/div/quote/quote[1]/label/#1"},"lb":{},"hi":{"@rend":"sc","#":{"value":"d’Espagne","id":"/div/quote/quote[1]/label/hi/#"}},"#2":{"value":".","id":"/div/quote/quote[1]/label/#2"}},"lg":{"l":[{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/quote[1]/lg/l[0]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Seconde Infante de Savoye,","id":"/div/quote/quote[1]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/quote[1]/lg/l[1]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dont le Pere est Victor Second,","id":"/div/quote/quote[1]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’un second fils de France, &amp; l’Epouse, &amp; la joye.","id":"/div/quote/quote[1]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quel presage d’un nom de cet auguste front !","id":"/div/quote/quote[1]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":[{"@rend":"sc","#":{"value":"Philippe","id":"/div/quote/quote[1]/lg/l[4]/hi[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"en